    <template id="welcome_article_body">
        <h1>
            <span>
                <strong>Agricultural Store</strong>
            </span>
        </h1>
        <p>
            <font color="#343541">Welcome to the <strong>
                    <font class="text-o-color-1">Odoo Agricultural Store package.</font>
                </strong></font>
        </p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">This solution is designed to manage every aspect of
            agricultural retail, supporting both <b>B2B and B2C sales</b> of farming products. It
            covers <b>Point of Sale (POS) and website</b> operations, offering organized categories
            like <b>seeds, pesticides, nutrition, and equipment</b>.
        </p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">It integrates essential Odoo modules, including <b>POS, Sales &amp; Purchase</b>. Utilizing the <b>Website and E-commerce</b>
            applications is key to accelerating growth in this sector.</p>
