                                    <div class="o_editor_banner_content o-contenteditable-true w-100 px-3" contenteditable="true">
                                        <p>
                                            <b>Use the</b>&#xFEFF;<a href="https://www.odoo.com/documentation/latest/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.html?highlight=seo">&#xFEFF;<b>
                    SEO features</b>&#xFEFF;</a>&#xFEFF; to improve your website's online visibility and
